---
title: Crusted Salmon and Bacon-Wrapped Asparagus with Parmesan-Potato Mash and Roasted Mushrooms
description: Bold Montreal-spiced salmon, seared to perfection, served with crispy bacon-wrapped asparagus and creamy Parmesan mashed potatoes. Finished with zesty horeradish cream sauce for the perfect balance of heat, richness and steakhouse-style indulgence.

